Latin America and Eastern Europe. Students in any subject area are eligible to apply if they demonstrate excellent school or academic merit wish to study in Germany and are committed to the values of social democracy. ','DE','Organización'),(46,'DAAD/Naumann','Alemania','The scholarship scheme is open to qualified international candidates with a first academic degree studying at German higher-education institutions for a Master\'s or a state examination degree. The minimum funding covers two semesters. Every year between 15 and 25 Master scholarships are awarded.','DE','Organización'),(47,'DAAD/Heinrich Böll','Alemania','Students from any discipline and higher-education institution are invited to apply for the scholarship by the Foundation which is closely associated with the German Green Party. Candidates have a positive attitude towards green ideals and academic standing and are socially and politically involved.','DE','Organización'),(48,'DAAD/Herzog August','Alemania','The Foundation awards sponsorships which are worth EUR 1 100/month for a period of two to 10 months. Fellows are accommodated in the library\'s Wolfenbüttel guest houses. The rent for the guest houses is paid from the grant sum. The grants include an allowance for material expenses of EUR 100/month','DE','Organización'),(49,'DAAD/KAS','Alemania','The Foundation awards every year about 50 scholarships to committed students/graduates and doctoral candidates. The Foundation\'s goal is to help further the education and training of academics expecting them to shoulder responsibility for the society in their home countries after their return.','DE','Organización'),(50,'DAAD/Rosa Luxemburg','Alemania','The RLF a political educational organisation closely affiliated with DIE LINKE (The Left Party) assigns scholarships to international students of graduate level planning to study in Germany.','DE','Organización'),(51,'DAAD/SDW','Alemania','The Foundation of German Business(SDW) offers undergraduate and graduate students a vast number of opportunities ranging from various seminars and training programmes. Courses are held in German so candidates should have at least intermediate-level command of German (B2 or DSH 2)','DE','Organización'),(52,'DAAD/Bavaria State','Alemania','The Max Weber Programme is open to particularly gifted high-school graduates and students who plan to study or are already enrolled at a Bavarian higher-education institution. Beyond the degree programme the scholarship holders are given the opportunity to participate in numerous events.','DE','Organización'),(53,'Universität Hamburg','Alemania','With its merit scholarship program Universität Hamburg supports outstanding international and doctoral students of all subjects and degree levels. The awarding of merit scholarships allows recipients to concentrate fully on their studies and gives them the opportunity to develop their skills.','DE','Organización'),(54,'Melbourne University','Nueva Zelanda','At the University of Melbourne we are proud of our outstanding reputation for excellence in teaching and research. Independently published world rankings consistently place us as a leader in higher education in Australia the Asia-Pacific and around the globe.','NZ','Escuela'),(55,'Macquarie University','Nueva Zelanda','Being a Macquarie student will be one of the best times of your life because you’ll have so many opportunities to discover your potential. As well as starting to carve out a fabulous career for yourself you’ll have opportunities to travel the globe with our support.','NZ','Escuela'),(56,'UTS','Nueva Zelanda','UTS is a dynamic and innovative university in central Sydney. One of Australia’s leading universities of technology UTS has a distinct model of learning strong research performance and a leading reputation for engagement with industry and the professions','NZ','Escuela'),(57,'Newcastle University','Nueva Zelanda','UON stands as a global leader distinguished by a commitment to equity and excellence and to creating a better future for its regions through a focus on innovation and impact.','NZ','Escuela'),(58,'Swinburne University','Nueva Zelanda','Students come first at Swinburne. Our courses are designed with your future in mind. Swinburne offers high-quality teaching opportunities to engage with industry state-of-the-art facilities and flexible study options.','NZ','Escuela'),(59,'UWA','Nueva Zelanda','For international students Perth is the perfect location with its warm sunny climate and relaxed outdoor lifestyle. Perth is also in the same time zone as many Asian countries making it easier to keep in touch with family and friends.','NZ','Escuela'),(60,'Auckland University','Nueva Zelanda','The only New Zealand university in the top 200 in the Times Higher Education World University. Also is in the top 100 and with the maximum rating in the QS Stars University Ratings. Finally the highest ranked New Zealand university in the Shanghai Jiao Tong Academic Ranking of World Universities.','NZ','Escuela'),(61,'Queensland Uni.','Nueva Zelanda','UQ is one of Australia’s leading research and teaching institutions. We strive for excellence through the creation preservation transfer and application of knowledge. For more than a century we have educated and worked with outstanding people to deliver knowledge leadership for a better world.','NZ','Escuela');
